+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01SzFcTUVhH2b2bkiSnT7nex","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Non-interactive mode: using Autopilot. The project structure is clear — empty module directories with type definitions already defined. Let me design and proceed directly to implementation.\n\nThe types.ts is comprehensive and defines all service interfaces. The design decisions are largely predetermined:\n\n1. **Registry**: In-memory store supporting multiple versions per plugin name\n2. **Resolver**: Wrap the `semver` npm package \n3. **Runner**: Node.js `vm` module with timeout support\n4. **Reviews**: better-sqlite3 for persistence\n5. **Deps**: Graph algorithms on registry data\n6. **Integration**: `createMarketplace()` composing all services\n\nLet me skip the full brainstorming formality since the requirements and interfaces are fully specified, and move directly to TDD implementation."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":693,"cache_read_input_tokens":24631,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":693},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"317a320e-f69c-41f4-82f8-3366e9d2c6c5","uuid":"4de5a7a4-14cc-4f6a-a1aa-917255747be0"}
